<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="be-about-to-do-sth">be about to do sth</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>正要 / 准备做某事：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I was about to turn off my computer when I received an email. 
我正准备关电脑,这时收到了一封电子邮件。</p><footer>2008 山东</footer></div>

<p>注: be about to常与when连用，表示“刚要…突然…”。  </p></div>